data.title: Dallas Symphony Orchestra
data.meta_description: The DSO Young Professionals build the next audience for the Dallas Symphony Orchestra by engaging and developing the passion for music in the future leaders of Dallas.
data.text:
Join the DSO YP

Join DSO YP with membership dues of $195. Experience the symphony with other Young Professionals through exclusive opportunities around DSO concerts, special events, and growing volunteer opportunities. DSO YP members are presented with at least one event per month throughout the DSO Season, so there is always an opportunity to mingle and engage.

Join now

DSO Young Professionals members receive:

These concerts include exclusive pre- and post-concert benefits such as a dedicated private YP space with dedicated YP member bar, musician meet and greets, private presentations and more. YP Members secure their complimentary concert ticket with s special promo code. Concerts include:

Stravinksy and Tchaikovsky | September 12, 2024

Ravel’s Bolero | November 14, 2024

Beethoven’s Fifth Symphony | February 7, 2025

A Night of Broadway | March 28, 2025

DSO YP members also have opportunities to peek behind the scenes of the Dallas Symphony and the music with special tours, previews of events and invitation only orchestra rehearsals. Our members will be able to have a drink with top Executives and meet DSO Musicians during Happy Hours, Concerts, Special YP Events and more.

DSO YP members receive an invitation to the black tie event marking the launch of the DSO Season, the DSO Gala and After Party.

DSO YP members receive additional discounts up to 50% off and complimentary tickets to select concerts throughout the season.

DSO YP Members are encourage to explore additional concerts with a specially curated Choose Your Own Subscription or a full Season Subscription with a special 15% discount. Choose Your Own Subscription includes four concerts of your choice through the DSO Season, although the DSO does have a few premade CYO subscriptions focusing on themes. Visit our calendar here to check out all the concerts this season.

DSO YP members receive a discount price on other YP events throughout the season.

2024-2025 DSO YP Calendar of Events

Every odd month we will host an informal gathering for members and inquiring members to meet and mingle over drinks. Periodically DSO Musicians are invited to join us for the fun. We enjoy exploring DFW and will alternate our venue each gathering. Follow us on social media to see more details on our locations or YP Members can check their emails. See dates below:

July 16, 2024 | Bach & Beer

September 17, 2024 | Bach & Beer

November 12, 2024 | Bach & Beer *special date due to the holidays

January 21, 2025 | Bach & Beer

March 28, 2025 | Bach & Beer

May 20, 2025 | Bach & Beer

DSO YP Members can cool off with us as we kick off the season, check your member email for all the details. Enjoy a complimentary beverage and small bites as we gather by the pool to celebrate summer and the start of the season.

Join us with your complimentary ticket via DSO YP Membership. A private intermission reception featuring small bites, complimentary wine, and cash bar for mixed drinks will welcome DSO YP members. Post-Concert members will gather at a nearby restaurant for a night-cap, YP Members check your text alerts to learn the venue.

Reserve your DSO YP Concert ticket here with your promo code.

Don’t forget to take advantage of your special DSO YP Gala Offer for the Concert and After-Party. The After-Party will feature music, drinks, and light nibbles.

More details to come soon.

Experience Steve Hackman’s thrilling new blend of pop/R&B’s queen and classical music’s king at this year’s DSO Young Professional Experience (DSO YP X). Listen as Beethoven’s Seventh Symphony becomes the perfect backdrop to fifteen of Beyoncé’s most popular songs including ‘Girls’, ‘Crazy in Love’, ‘Sorry’, ‘Halo’, ‘Cuff It”, ‘Single Ladies’ and of course ‘Texas Hold ‘Em’.

Learn more here.

Become a Young Professional Stradivarius Patron

Join the Stradivarius Patron Society with a special Young Professional 50% offer*. With your commitment of $1,500, you will be joining an important group of DSO patrons who enjoy elevated experiences and behind-the-scenes access all season long.
